social_posts.post_text: Thank you, Adventurers. 🙏🏼💚 @spotify defines our listeners as “seekers of sound. They venture out into the unknown, searching for fresh artists, deep cuts, new tracks - especially gems yet to be found.” We love that and you. 💚 Here’s to more music in 2023 🥂
Look Ma, we’re bobbleheads. Singing bobbleheads who took a little cruise down the Sunset Strip. This was our last single before the Holidays, Sunset Blvd. If you need a little rewind to Summer. 🌞

Meet M3GAN, soundtracked by our song “Le Point Zéro.” 🔪 We’re so thrilled to have a song from our French album in this new horror movie from director Gerard Johnstone and producers creepypuppet & @itsjasonblum. We can’t to hear it loud in theaters (Jan 6). Thanks to music supervisor Andrea von Foerster and anyone on the music department. Are you guys as excited as we are to see this movie?
#m3gan #blumhouse #freedomfry #m3gansoundtrack

If David Bowie’s “Starman” was a Christmas song. 🎅🏼⛄️👨🏻‍🎤
#davidbowie #cover #starman #christmas #christmassong #reels #freedomfry
Merry Merry everyone! ❄️🎄#dec24 #christmaseve #xmas

Here’s a look back at our 2022. We put out a lot of music and it popped up in some pretty cool places. Thanks for being a part of our journey. Happy New Year everyone! ✌🏼❤️
#reels #freedomfry #2022 #m3gan #newmusicfriday #playlists #lookback #2022goals #happynewyear
It’s #M3GAN day. 💃🏼🔪 We’re so excited our song, “Le Point Zéro,” is in the film. The reviews have been insane. Currently at 95% on @rottentomatoes. Let us know if you see it. 🙌🏼

If The World Was Mine. Our first single of 2023. Coming Feb 1. Pre-save it at the #linkinbio For now here’s a #teaser
#freedomfry #newmusic

Take a trip back to the ‘90s. This just came out on @netflix today. Bruce worked with @jamesihaofficial @_dougclarke on cues for this. Also with @kielfeher and @brettelizabethanderson on the theme song. We hope it gets you all nostalgic for vhs and flannel. 📼

✨New Music Alert✨ “I know that if the world was mine the sun would always shine, and all the trees would dance in line, the days would be so fine.” 🌞 ‘If the World Was Mine,’ our first single of 2023 is at your favorite place to listen. @spotify @applemusic @deezer @amazonmusic. The full length version of this visual is at the #LinkInBio. Up next, more French songs. Stay tuned. ✌🏼💙

Hearing your song on the radio will never get old. Huge thank you @nicharcourt @thesocalsound @jet_ontheair for always championing our music. We ❤️ ya. #freshsqueezedtrackoftheday 
#freedomfry #radio #nicharcourt #885 #freedomfrymusic
When you get to be in a band with your Valentine 💘

Good things on the way 💙❤️ 
📷 @michelleshiers

Ooh La La. We’re going back to French. On March 22 “Je T’aime Pas, Je T’aime” (which translates to ‘I don’t love you, I love you’) will be coming your way @spotify @applemusic @bandcamp. You can #PreSave it at the #linkinbio. This is the first single from a French EP we just put the finishing touches on. We’re so excited for you to hear all the tracks. Stay tuned.

#freedomfry #freedomfrymusic #jetaime #frenchpop #newmusic

♥︎New Music Alert♥︎ ‘Je T’aime Pas, Je T’aime’ is now streamable everywhere you listen @Spotify @Bandcamp @AppleMusic. #linkinbio We hope it gets you feeling good. By the way, there’s a b-side too if you feel like going crazy. x
📷 @michelleshiers
Do not be fooled by the expression on our faces. We’re stoked about our new song out ! We were just not as ecstatic about standing in the rain
The video for Je T’aime Pas, Je T’aime is here! Catch the full thing at the #linkinbio.

“The world is a vampire.” We just dropped a new acoustic cover of @smashingpumpkins under Marie’s name. We love releasing covers and this is where a lot of our future ones will end up, so follow Marie Seyrat on @spotify and @applemusic so you get them on your Release Radar. For the next one we’re thinking @neworderofficial. 💙
…
📷 @michelleshiers 
#newmusic #smashingpumpkins #freedomfry #marieseyrat #spotify #covers

Despite all my rage I am still just a rat in a cage. A new visual for @marie.Seyrat’s cover of @smashingpumpkins is now on our Freedom Fry YT channel. Follow her at @spotify and @applemusic because there are more covers on the way.
…
#freedomfry #newmusic #cover #smashingpumpkins

The sun’s out and you need a new wardrobe ? Well, this may be your lucky day… We have new shirts for ya ! We’re hoping to extend the line here and there with lyrics and more designs, but go check out what we have for now ! ~ Link in bio ~

🚨New Music🚨 “Le Parapluie” which translates to “The Umbrella” is a modern spin on the idea of ditching your umbrella and dancing in the rain. Trying to find the positive in the negative and roll with the punches. We wanted to make it funky like some bands we love from the ‘70s. It’s named after an umbrella but it’s 100% a song for a sunny day. Link in bio.
Artwork by @noemiferst @monsieurmoru

Elle Est, pronounced “L.A.” but meaning ‘She Is’ is a French love letter to Los Angeles. It’s the b-side to Le Parapluie. Now streaming @spotify @spotifyfrance @applemusic @bandcamp and more. This is some footage from The Chateau Marmont, when we recorded our song “West Coast.”
Thanks for adding Le Parapluie to these rad playlists @spotify @applemusic 🧡
Here’s a demo version of our song You Know the Way. I kinda miss these drums. Let us know if we should release this version too.

New video 👀 This diy one involved staying very still, resting our chins on a green screen, and then keying it all out. If anyone wants to make a game of pong with our heads and an 8-bit version of this song that would 🔥 #leparapluie #linkinbio

Are you ready for the party? ‘La Soirée,’ the final single from the EP of the same name is now @Spotify @AppleMusic @Bandcamp. The full EP is coming Friday. For bonus points check out the b-side, “Alex,” too. It’s inspired by A Clockwork Orange. 
… Artwork by @noemiferst @monsieurmoru

The La Soirée EP is here. Just in time for going out or staying in on Fryday night. All the past six French singles from this year compiled in one spot. Give them a stream at your favorite place to listen and join the party. Thanks to @SpotifyFrance for adding “La Soirée” to New Music Friday France. And thanks to @AppleMusic for adding it to the New In Indie playlist. We hope you dig it. What’s your favorite track?
… Drawings by @noemiferst @monsieurmoru
“La Soirée” now has a visual you can vibe to. #LinkInBio.
It’s @brucedriscoll ‘s birthday today and if you know him, you’re one of the lucky ones. Happy Birthday Bruce !! You’re one in a million, we love you 🧡

After picking up a BAFTA and a Broadcast Award for its first season, Lovely Little Farm, the live-action and animated hybrid series we scored for @AppleTV @DarrallMacqueen is back for Season 2! We’re especially proud of this season because it has even more songs we wrote that the characters actually sing! Pickle Pony (brilliantly voiced by @dominiqueamoore), Al Alpaca (Joel Fry), and the rest of the brilliant cast @obviouslykassidi, Levi Howden, Shirley Henderson & all did a fantastic job. For those, like us, who feel like most family shows these days are are over the top and intense, this is the antidote for that. You actually feel like you’ve taken a trip to a serene farm while watching. We hope you enjoy it! 
…
#lovelylittlefarm

Meet Me in Paris. We met @lilseyiofficial and instantly hit it off. After an initial conversation we sent him some ideas and we were blown away by what he sent back. The first of two singles we wrote together is out today. Hear “Meet Me in Paris” wherever you like to stream 🎧.
Fill My Cup, our second collab with @lilseyiofficial is now @spotify @applemusic
We ❤️ you Jane. This autograph has become an even more treasured momento. #RIP
Here’s a New Order cover for you. @marie.seyrat has an extra haunting, acoustic take on the classic, Blue Monday. Stream it @spotify @applemusic or wherever you listen.
3D in Paris
YOLO, our new single, just arrived @spotify @applemusic @bandcamp. Seize the day and get down to it wherever you like to listen.
Thanks @spotify curators for adding YOLO to Good Vibes. And to @deezer for adding it to Indie Electro. 🖤🖤🖤🙏🏼🙏🏼🙏🏼
Photo Booths in Montmartre ❤️
Pieces of Summer. Paris & LA.
Coming to the rescue 🦸🏼‍♀️ “Rescue” is out today @spotify @applemusic. Add it your favorite playlist and save the day.
It’s Fryday! “Rescue” is out now @spotify @applemusic @bandcamp & more. 😘

Our debut album Classic came out five years ago. 😱 Also, because we’re getting close to Halloween, here’s a clip from the short horror short film RNP by our insanely talented friend, writer/director/actor @jesilerae. Two girls, Jesi and @margauxbrooke, wind up at an Airbnb and some craziness goes down. 🔪 Here’s a clip with the acoustic version of our song, “Classic.”
🎥  @ivanstekovich
Have a good weekend everybody 💚

We’re down to play your Halloween parties 👻 🎃 
This is our song, “Zombie Love,” from a few years back.

✨✨Dreamland✨✨ “Now I’m walking in a dreamland, far away, yeah, I’m so far away, been since I met you now.” New today and listenable @spotify @applemusic, etc.  Get that floating feeling and add it to your favorite playlist.

Top o the morning to ya 🌞
Chestnuts roasting on an open 🔥. Got something merry for ya today to give a brief respite from this heavy world. You know where to look 👀. 🎅🏼 🌲
Thanks @spotify for adding The Christmas Song to this very merry playlist. 🎄 Also feat. @laufey, @cher, @jimmyfallon, @sabrinacarpenter.
Thanks for streaming us you lovely people. We are grateful for you and have lots more music on the way. #spotifywrapped
We upped the energy on 15 Freedom Fry fan favorites. Get down to High Speed for all your workout, dancing, social media posts, or whenever you need a pick-me-up. Hear it wherever you like to listen.

Vibe out with Freedom Fry for the holidays. We’ve put all our Xmas songs in one playlist.
